="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=pzeLAIhFMIU:hjzEzVTflAg:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=pzeLAIhFMIU:hjzEzVTflAg:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=pzeLAIhFMIU:hjzEzVTflAg:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=pzeLAIhFMIU:hjzEzVTflAg:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/pzeLAIhFMIU" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:14;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:51:"Premium WordPress Plugin â€“ Top Social Share Posts";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/3AlS0z6eu6Q/";s:8:"comments";s:120:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Wed, 08 Feb 2012 07:48:01 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:3:"Lee";}s:8:"category";s:147:"Social NetworksWordpress Pluginsaccordiongoogle +1jQuerylinkedinpin itpinterestpluginspremiumsocial mediasocial networksstumbleupontwitterwordpress";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=2614";s:11:"description";s:724:"<p><img src="/media/images/top_social_share_posts.png" alt="Top Social Share Posts WordPress Plugin" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Now you can list most popular posts according to social shares/likes.</p>\n<p>With full support for Facebook, Twitter, Google +1, Linkedin, Digg, Delicious, Stumbleupon, Reddit &#038; Pinterest it offers a great range of options for promoting both your content and your social networks.</p>\n<p>Go to plugin demo &#038; home page or Purchase at Codecanyon.</p>\nTop Social Share Posts Demo Pages\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Top </li> &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/" class="read_more">more</a></ul>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:5486:"<p><img src="/media/images/top_social_share_posts.png" alt="Top Social Share Posts WordPress Plugin" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Now you can list most popular posts according to social shares/likes.</p>\n<p>With full support for Facebook, Twitter, Google +1, Linkedin, Digg, Delicious, Stumbleupon, Reddit &#038; Pinterest it offers a great range of options for promoting both your content and your social networks.</p>\n<p><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/" class="underline">Go to plugin demo &#038; home page</a> or <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/top-social-share-posts/1538572?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">Purchase at Codecanyon</a>.</p>\n<h3>Top Social Share Posts Demo Pages</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/">Top Social Share Posts Carousel &#038; Accordion</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/top-post-for-each-social-network/">Top Post For Each Social Network</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/total-social-shares/">Total Social Share Statistics</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/top-social-posts-by-post-type/">Top Social Posts By Post Type</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/top-social-posts-by-category/">Top Social Posts by Category</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/using-shortcodes/">Example Using Shortcodes</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The plugin includes 2 easy to use widgets:</p>\n<h3>Top Social Share Posts</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Show top posts by social network.</li>\n<li>Display using built-in jQuery accordion widget or a slick carousel.</li>\n<li>Option to display total share counts for all networks.</li>\n<li>Option to list all share counts for each post.</li>\n<li>Option to include excerpt in post lists.</li>\n<li>Filter by category using the built-in shortcode version.</li>\n<li>Include custom post types and display top custom post shares.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Top Social Share Statistics</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Add a new widget to your site displaying your total shares per network.</li>\n<li>Also includes option to add a grand total for all social shares</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Plugin Options &#038; Admin Statistics</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Automatically identifies your custom post types.</li>\n<li>Adds option to include custom post types in the share data &#038; widgets.</li>\n<li>Enable/disable networks via plugin settings.</li>\n<li>Add your own custom social network icons.</li>\n<li>Advanced settings for controlling data updates and caching.</li>\n<li>Option to cache widget results to minimize loading time</li>\n<li>Limit age of posts included in social share counts.</li>\n<li>&#8220;Update All&#8221; button for mass update of share counts.</li>\n<li>Color pickers and custom CSS field for customising front-end widgets.</li>\n<li>Preview widgets in plugin options page.</li>\n<li>Plugin includes full documentation &#038; inline admin help.</li>\n<li>Social statistics page in admin provides complete overview of all post data.</li>\n<li>Sort by date, title or social network &#038; filtter by category or post type</li>\n<li>View data using jQuery data heatmap.</li>\n<li>Update individual post share data via statistics table.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Top Social Share Posts finally adds the ability to list your most popular posts according to social network shares/likes.</p>\n<p><a href="