/span></p>\n<h3><strong>WP Late Night airs live every Wednesday at 8pm Eastern. <a href="http://wpcandy.com/stream">Tune in tonight!</a></strong></h3>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:75:"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/09/26/have-you-tuned-into-wp-late-night/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:44:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:40:"WordCamp Grand Rapids is just days away!";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/08/16/wordcamp-grand-rapids-is-just-days-away/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:85:"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/08/16/wordcamp-grand-rapids-is-just-days-away/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 16 Aug 2012 20:24:11 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"WordCamp";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"Grand Rapids";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:32:"http://webdevstudios.com/?p=6725";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:322:"WordCamp is coming to Grand Rapids, MI this weekend! In just 2 days, Grand Valley State University will be overrun with WordPress enthusiasts spreading lots of WordPress love.  <a href="http://webdevstudios.com/2012/08/16/wordcamp-grand-rapids-is-just-days-away/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"April Heline";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2216:"<p><a href="http://2012.grandrapids.wordcamp.org/"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-6714" title="WCGR12-WebBanners-Sponsor" src="http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/WCGR12-WebBanners-Sponsor.png" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></a>WordCamp is coming to Grand Rapids, MI this weekend! In just 2 days, Grand Valley State University will be overrun with WordPress enthusiasts spreading lots of WordPress love.</p>\n<p>The Grand Rapids organizers have worked hard to provide everyone with a jam-packed two days of WordPress goodness.</p>\n<p>Saturday, there will be <a href="http://2012.grandrapids.wordcamp.org/schedule/">4 tracks</a> full of awesome <a href="http://2012.grandrapids.wordcamp.org/speakers/">speakers</a> that want to share their WordPress knowledge and expertise with you. Â The Saturday conference will be followed by an afterparty at the <a href="http://2012.grandrapids.wordcamp.org/2012/08/15/party-up/" target="_blank">SpeakEZ Lounge</a>.</p>\n<p>Sunday is <a href="http://2012.grandrapids.wordcamp.org/2012/08/16/what-is-wordpress-study-hall/">WordPress Study Hall</a> where the Grand Rapids organizers are combining the Â traditional â€œDev Dayâ€ that follows most WordCamp events with more user- and attendee-focused opportunities.</p>\n<p>Haven&#8217;t got a ticket yet? Don&#8217;t worry becauseÂ <a href="http://2012.grandrapids.wordcamp.org/attend/">75 additional tickets</a> were released yesterday and there are plenty still up for grabs! Grand Rapids a little to far for you to travel? You can <a href="http://2012.grandrapids.wordcamp.org/2012/08/14/cant-make-it-but-still-want-to-join-in-the-fun/">tune in</a>Â remotely via a developer track livestream.</p>\n<p>For more information on WordCamp Grand Rapids, check out the <a href="http://2012.grandrapids.wordcamp.org/">website</a>Â or follow them onÂ <a href="https://twitter.com/wcgrandrapids/">Twitter</a>.</p>\n<p>Last, we want to give a shout out to our newest WDS team member, <a href="http://webdevstudios.com/team/brian-richards/">Brian Richards</a>, and the organizers who have done so much hard work and planning to bring WordCamp to Western Michigan. We know it&#8217;s going to be a great event!</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:81:"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/08/16/wordcamp-grand-rapids-is-just-days-away/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:47:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s: